api_list.name: Convert PDF (base64) to ZPL
api_list.description: Receives a PDF base64 and returns the desired ZPL code.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://anttools.p.rapidapi.com/convert/pdf/to/zpl"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "anttools.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
